---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="关于我们 - 职场避雷针" description="了解职场避雷针平台的背景、使命和价值观">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="mb-8 text-center">关于我们</h1>
    
    <!-- 平台介绍 -->
    <section class="mb-12 card">
      <h2 class="mb-4">平台介绍</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p>
          职场避雷针（CompanyBlacklist）是一个公益性质的企业违规行为曝光平台，旨在帮助职场人士规避不良企业，维护自身合法权益。
        </p>
        <p>
          我们的使命是建立一个透明、公正、可信赖的职场信息共享平台，让求职者能够更全面地了解企业，做出更明智的职业选择。
        </p>
        <p>
          所有信息都经过严格的双重审核（初审志愿者 + 终审管理员），确保信息的真实性和客观性。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- 使命与价值观 -->
    <section class="mb-12 card">
      <h2 class="mb-4">使命与价值观</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 12 10 12-4.48 12-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            使命
          </h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>建立透明、公正的职场信息共享平台</li>
            <li>帮助职场人士规避不良企业</li>
            <li>维护职场人士的合法权益</li>
            <li>推动企业规范经营</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 12 10 12-4.48 12-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            价值观
          </h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>真实：所有信息经过严格审核</li>
            <li>公正：客观中立，不偏不倚</li>
            <li>透明：审核流程公开透明</li>
            <li>公益：免费为职场人士服务</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- 如何贡献 -->
    <section class="mb-12 card">
      <h2 class="mb-4">如何贡献</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3">参与方式</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              提交企业爆料，帮助其他职场人士
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              参与审核，确保信息的真实性
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              反馈问题或提出改进建议
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              分享平台，让更多人受益
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3">赞助支持</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">如果您觉得本项目有帮助，欢迎通过以下方式支持我们：</p>
          <a href="https://afdian.com/a/Ableand" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-purple-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-600 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"></path>
            </svg>
            爱发电赞助
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- 常见问题 -->
    <section class="card">
      <h2 class="mb-4">常见问题</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-8-3a1 1 0 00-.867.5 1 1 0 11-1.731-1A3 3 0 0113 8a3.001 3.001 0 01-2 2.83V11a1 1 0 11-2 0v-1a1 1 0 011-1 1 1 0 100-2zm0 8a1 1 0 100-2 1 1 0 000 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <strong class="block">如何提交企业爆料？</strong>
            <p class="text-sm">请通过 <a href="https://github.com/CompanyBlacklist/CompanyBlacklist/issues/new?template=report.yml" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">GitHub Issues</a> 提交，我们会在 24 小时内回复。</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-8-3a1 1 0 00-.867.5 1 1 0 11-1.731-1A3 3 0 0113 8a3.001 3.001 0 01-2 2.83V11a1 1 0 11-2 0v-1a1 1 0 011-1 1 1 0 100-2zm0 8a1 1 0 100-2 1 1 0 000 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <strong class="block">如何参与审核？</strong>
            <p class="text-sm">请通过 <a href="https://github.com/CompanyBlacklist/CompanyBlacklist/issues/new?template=reviewer.yml" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">GitHub Issues</a> 申请成为审核志愿者，我们会进行审核。</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-8-3a1 1 0 00-.867.5 1 1 0 11-1.731-1A3 3 0 0113 8a3.001 3.001 0 01-2 2.83V11a1 1 0 11-2 0v-1a1 1 0 011-1 1 1 0 100-2zm0 8a1 1 0 100-2 1 1 0 000 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <strong class="block">如何举报不实信息？</strong>
            <p class="text-sm">请通过 <a href="https://github.com/CompanyBlacklist/CompanyBlacklist/issues/new?template=appeal.yml" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">企业申诉</a> 提交，我们会进行核实。</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
